{"hash":"6108dce83f84adf5e48d152551276a9d17331918","data":{"post":{"title":"Introduction to Gridsome","date":"April 8, 2019","content":"<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1024 576' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-b444e3356503589a3a85e516e7b0fbc7'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-b444e3356503589a3a85e516e7b0fbc7)' width='1024' height='576' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bbehXGfrpHhOY5K5KB/wCmtLXEyai5sURpjbpwG3vpr7KGSk/0e4phrvpBg76GouLcczHG1MwUtKbiNSFSGjwqVlQzyJAI7GrX8LLW6i9okpnOtxnEEBtIPC4vG6Fegxueu21LXfW%2bjLxdHXJ%2bnJyoSlKKEtuoQpoFIHlx/qP2a7kfEOxWWOI2ibdLaaW0eMTVDCHPQpGTnnufXA2oq74zpsVTk%2bmPf4mqaa6lLQ7Hhe3sf7NdRH2qA13LlWjTUmVBQ6qSkp4OBvjxvkk9sVVLD8Wm1W6Sb1GS1IQkJZUweIOKxvkHlvj94qb0Lq6XqiaWHFQm2RHWoIKuF51WPRJ6YJOM7Yqgsp1GnJssXKr385eN1Kq1dqNgn%2bTLomobuvUrL79zeQpakqWVg8DfUcGwVgE7fnnW/oZ8ieIgqwMkcjVO19ZtNquNpbkzWYUpLoKg0tJ4EYGSof4jygb9TV/tgauMNuTb1h%2bOoeVSN%2b2/T3oLqnVUauu1FKg58MenMhoWNJcO%2befvGCmRTG6wPm4TzCTwKUnyq%2b1XMH2OKe6kukDTsXx7o4pscwhKSpZGcZA965sU%2bJfbeJkDxfCKikhxBSoHuDVYutuCC/adue/hmWI1KMdhM%2bT6BRRXUZz6e0vFlPxStUZ5xpS0FtRQrBKTzH4NFFMQCMGIHHaIZp5Euc%2bGngiTZLCCclLTqkg%2bwNFFOyhhhhmIEjkR1cdR3q4pbTPukyQlvIR4jpPCM5/tLR9WX%2bNb1wmrvMEVfNsuZ7czuP3RRWE6akjaUGB5CTW1wchj%2b5//2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"1024\" alt=\"background\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/blog_bg.82a2fbd.a07cff5f4273a1d6ec3e440574567395.jpg 480w, /assets/static/blog_bg.cbab2cf.a07cff5f4273a1d6ec3e440574567395.jpg 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/blog_bg.cbab2cf.a07cff5f4273a1d6ec3e440574567395.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/blog_bg.cbab2cf.a07cff5f4273a1d6ec3e440574567395.jpg\" width=\"1024\" alt=\"background\"></noscript></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Gridsome is a Vue.js-powered, modern site generator for building the fastest possible websites for any Headless CMS, APIs or Markdown-files. Gridsome makes it easy and fun for developers to create fast, beautiful websites without needing to become a performance expert.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"why-gridsome\"><a href=\"#why-gridsome\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Why Gridsome?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Local development with hot-reloading</strong> - See code changes in real-time.</li>\n<li><strong>Data source plugins</strong> - Use it for any popular Headless CMSs, APIs or Markdown-files.</li>\n<li><strong>File-based page routing</strong> - Quickly create and manage routes with files.</li>\n<li><strong>Centralized data managment</strong> - Pull data into a local, unified GraphQL data layer.</li>\n<li><strong>Vue.js for frontend</strong> - A lightweight and approachable front-end framework.</li>\n<li><strong>Auto-optimized code</strong> - Get code-splitting and asset optimization out-of-the-box.</li>\n<li><strong>Static files generation</strong> - Deploy securely to any CDN or static web host.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/docs/how-it-works\">Learn more about how Gridsome works</a></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">template</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">  &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">Layout</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">    &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">class=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">container-inner mx-auto my-16</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">      &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">class=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">text-4xl font-bold leading-tight</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;{{ $page.post.</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">title</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> }}&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">h1</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">      &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">class=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;{{ $page.post.</span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">date</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> }}&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">      &lt;</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">class=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">markdown-body</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">v-html=</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">$page.post.content</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\"> /&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">    &lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">div</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">  &lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">Layout</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color: #F07178\">template</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"prerequisites\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Prerequisites</h3>\n<p>You should have basic knowledge about HTML, CSS, <a href=\"https://vuejs.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vue.js</a> and how to use the <a href=\"https://www.linode.com/docs/tools-reference/tools/using-the-terminal/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Terminal</a>. Knowing how <a href=\"https://vuejs.org/v2/guide/single-file-components.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vue Single File components</a> &#x26; <a href=\"https://www.graphql.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GraphQL</a> works is a plus, but not required. Gridsome is a great way to learn both.</p>\n<p>Gridsome requires <strong>Node.js</strong> and recommends <strong>Yarn</strong>. <a href=\"/docs/prerequisites\">How to setup</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-install-gridsome-cli-tool\"><a href=\"#1-install-gridsome-cli-tool\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. Install Gridsome CLI tool</h3>\n<p>Using yarn:\n<code>yarn global add @gridsome/cli</code></p>\n<p>Using npm:\n<code>npm install --global @gridsome/cli</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-create-a-gridsome-project\"><a href=\"#2-create-a-gridsome-project\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. Create a Gridsome project</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><code>gridsome create my-gridsome-site</code> to create a new project </li></li>\n<li><code>cd my-gridsome-site</code> to open folder</li>\n<li><code>gridsome develop</code> to start local dev server at <code>http://localhost:8080</code></li>\n<li>Happy coding 🎉🙌</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"3-next-steps\"><a href=\"#3-next-steps\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>3. Next steps</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Create <code>.vue</code> components in the <code>/pages</code> directory to create page routes.</li>\n<li>Use <code>gridsome build</code> to generate static files in a <code>/dist</code> folder</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/how-it-works\">How it works</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/pages\">How Pages work</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/deployment\">How to deploy</a></li>\n</ul>\n","tags":[{"title":"frontend","path":"/tag/frontend/"},{"title":"coding","path":"/tag/coding/"},{"title":"vue","path":"/tag/vue/"}]}},"context":{}}